30/05/2005
NICOSIA, Cyprus -- UN Undersecretary General for Political Affairs Kieran Prendergast began a visit to Cyprus on Monday (30 May). He will meet separately with political leaders from both sides of the divided island, including Cypriot President Tassos Papadopoulos and Turkish Cypriot leader Mehmet Ali Talat, as well as leaders of local political parties. He then travels on to Athens and Ankara. (Kathimerini - 30/05/05)
